# .claude_plans Directory

This directory stores project planning documents.

## Recommended Files

- `projectplan.md` - Main project roadmap and task tracking
- `phase1_plan.md`, `phase2_plan.md`, etc. - Phase-specific detailed plans
- `architecture_decisions.md` - Architecture Decision Records (ADRs)
- `research_notes.md` - Research findings and analysis

## Usage

1. Create `projectplan.md` before starting any significant work
2. Break down work into checkpoints with measurable success criteria
3. Update plans as tasks are completed
4. Add review sections after each phase

## Template

```markdown
# Project Plan: [Feature/Project Name]

## Overview
[Brief description of what we're building]

## Phase 1: [Phase Name]

### Checkpoint 1.1: [Name]
- [ ] Task 1
- [ ] Task 2

**Success Criteria:**
- [Measurable criterion]

### Checkpoint 1.2: [Name]
- [ ] Task 3

## Review
[Added after completion with summary of changes]
```
